data.description: If you've been looking for an immaculate riverfront home, this one is definitely one you don't want to miss! This private retreat is nestled on 13+ acres located on a high bluff overlooking the Savannah River. Features include a formal dining room, spacious great room w/a gas fireplace, built-ins & custom cabinetry, recessed lighting, whole house Generac generator, bonus room upstairs, oversized walk-in attic, new duct work, new insulation & a variety of fruit trees. The kitchen boasts Corian countertops, gas range, tile back splash & stainless-steel appliances, a breakfast bar, pantry & breakfast area. Enjoy outdoor entertaining at its finest relaxing on the large screen porch overlooking the high bluff. Workshop complete with electricity & pole barn with automatic garage doors. Imagine rocking on your covered front porch surrounded by tranquil scenery & nature that this slice of heaven has to offer. Get away from it all and enjoy coming home to your own little riverfront paradise!
